## Editor screen rules

- Editor route is outside AppShell — has its own full-screen layout.
- Left panel visual style must match Library/Device exactly:
  same sidebar bg, same Divider component, same section label style
  (text-sm font-light uppercase tracking-wide text-text-muted pl-6).
- Zone color ≠ LED color. Zone color = canvas visual only.
  LED color = preset gradient (colorA + colorB).
- No MIDI Learn — removed from MVP scope, do not add it.
- Scale is preset-level, not per-zone.
- Fan canvas is SVG-based. Zones are SVG path elements (arc sectors).
  Fan originates from bottom-center of the canvas area.
